Tumhare paas ek bag (knapsack) hai jisme maximum weight W tak ka samaan aa sakta hai. Tumhare paas n items hain, har ek ka:

weight w[i]

value v[i]

Tumhe decide karna hai kaunsa item lena hai aur kaunsa nahi, taaki total value maximum ho aur weight limit cross na ho.

0/1 ka matlab:

Har item ya to lo (1) ya na lo (0). Fraction nahi le sakte.
